HEADWORD: Graille
<hw>Graille</hw> <pr>(gr⟦amac⟧l)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>gr⟦ecir⟧le</ets> a sort of file.]</ety> <def>A halfround single-cut
